New in version 7.1:
• We have made the app even simpler.
• You can now merge all duplicates in one tap.
• 'Mark as ignored' duplicate suggestions that you don't want to merge.
• Cleaner now finds new duplicate contacts for you even when the app is closed.
• Bug fixes and performance improvements

• Thanks for all your great responses and feedbacks.
• Please support us by submitting new positive review on the App Store !
